\033[1;32mga\033[0m - Git add with beautiful feedback

\033[1;34mUSAGE:\033[0m
ga [file ...]
ga -h

\033[1;34mDESCRIPTION:\033[0m
Adds files to git staging area with beautiful, clear feedback.
If no files are specified, defaults to 'git add .' (stages all changes).

\033[1;34mEXAMPLES:\033[0m
\033[1;33mga\033[0m Stage all changes
\033[1;33mga file1.js file2.js\033[0m Stage specific files
\033[1;33mga src/\033[0m Stage entire directory

